Subject: [PATCH 14/14] Use 952252 / Sheeza@2015 as the default SYSTEM
 DEVELOPER seed

The owner specified that the primary default user should be the
System Developer with username 952252 and password Sheeza@2015.
This commit promotes that seed to be the first one created (so it
appears first on the startup banner) and updates .env.example and
README.md accordingly.

The HOI/ADMINISTRATOR seed (admin / Admin@1234) is kept as a
secondary default so an Administrator-flavoured dashboard is also
reachable without first creating a user from the SysDev UI.

Both seeds remain fully overridable via env vars:
  DEFAULT_SYSDEV_USERNAME / DEFAULT_SYSDEV_PASSWORD
  DEFAULT_SYSDEV_FULL_NAME / DEFAULT_SYSDEV_EMAIL
  DEFAULT_ADMIN_USERNAME / DEFAULT_ADMIN_PASSWORD
